 reply.  On Karana you should be able to get one fairly easily for 15k and if you hold out perhaps for 10k or less.</P><P></P><P><a href="www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=235322" target="_blank">Zetapsi Kappaphi</a> - 54 Dark-elf (always minus the elf) Necromonster <BR>The Watchmen... of Karana<BR>(click name for Magelo profile)</font></td>
